{"type":"question","id":12957,"title":"为什么说没有共蟾党就没有新中国？","uid":7290,"topics":[5,14,25,401],"contents":"常说<b>「没有共蟾党就没有新中国」</b>，但庆丰年间习炀帝大肆迫害共蟾党人，使绝大多数蛤蟆功学员身陷囹圄，更有威风八面一身虎胆的徐才厚大将军惨遭杀害。既然我们的包子如此仇视共蟾党人，这句歌词是不是在阴阳怪气我们的伟大领袖吸茎瓶主席？<br>\n<a href=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EklK0o1UUAA2RfV?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EklK0o1UUAA2RfV?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" alt=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/EklK0o1UUAA2RfV?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-10-19","agreeCount":7,"discussionCount":0}